地點：天水圍西面明渠旁，鄰近[[天瑞邨|天瑞邨]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UpBt-OgFe_I |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2017-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213131121/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UpBt-OgFe_I |dead-url=no }}</ref>
營業時間：每天早上5時至7時<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110315/00176_097.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-02-09 |archive-date=2012-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107065914/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110315/00176_097.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
